headline: 5 P&C Insurers to Watch Amid Soft Pricing, Low Interest Rate
summary: Zacks Property and Casualty Insurance players like PGR, CB, TRV, ALL and ACGL are likely to benefit from catastrophes that drive policy renewal rate and pricing.

headline: Arch Capital Group Ltd. Appoints Alexander Moczarski to Board of Directors
summary: PEMBROKE, Bermuda, February 06, 2025--Arch Capital Group Ltd. (NASDAQ: ACGL) ("Arch" or the "Company") today announced Alexander "Alex" Moczarski has joined the Company’s Board of Directors, effective immediately.
